January 2024
Zapier's Latest
Build automation-first tables and web pages that connect to your Zaps. Here are the latest product updates, apps, and news for January.
Automation Platform
Build unstoppable workflows
Every Zapier account now has access to Interfaces and Tables. Bonus: Tasks you automate using Tables or Interfaces won't count toward your Zapier plan limit.
Find out how
Product updates
New features to try now
Comment in Canvas, add conditional logic to Interfaces forms, and view Chatbot conversation histories! Plus, see your HTTP logs for Zap errors.
See what's new
Plan updates
Unlock more Zaps, more value
ICYMI: Build unlimited Zaps on all Zapier plans, tasks are free for select Zapier features, and pay per task when you exceed your plan limit.
Learn more
Zapier Canvas
Now in beta: Zapier Canvas
Visualize, plan, and create automated systems with your Zaps, Tables, and Interfaces-powered by AI.
Try it now
Level up your automation
Updated: Build workflows with Tables
Not sure how to make the most of Tables? You'll learn best practices for connecting data with Zaps to create your own approvals workflow.
Grow your skills
New: Automate full systems on Zapier
This course will teach you how to use Zaps, Tables, and Interfaces to build a your own lead management app.
Build and learn
Webinar: Keap + Zapier
Join us on February 7 to learn how to close any gaps by automating all your processes with Keap powered by Zapier.
Register now
